Season salmon, if desired, with salt and pepper. Melt 1 tablespoon Spread in large nonstick skillet over medium-high heat and cook salmon, turning occasionally, until salmon flakes with a fork, about 5 minutes. Remove and set aside. Melt remaining 1 tablespoon Spread in same skillet over medium-high heat and cook green beans and garlic, stirring occasionally, until fragrant, about 2 minutes. Prepare Knorr(R) Rice Sides(TM) - Herb & Butter in same skillet according to package directions. Stir in parsley, lemon juice and salmon. Serve, if desired, with lemon wedges.